---
const personalImageAlt = "Daniel Alejandro";
---

<article class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-8 lg:gap-12 xl:gap-16">
  
  {/* Texto */}
  <div class="flex-1 space-y-6 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed order-2 lg:order-1">
    
    <p class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900/30 rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-800">
      <span class="text-2xl mr-2">👋</span> 
      My name is 
      <strong class="bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-600 to-red-600 dark:from-orange-400 dark:to-red-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
        Daniel Alejandro
      </strong> 
      (my friends call me 
      <strong class="text-orange-600 dark:text-orange-400">Daga</strong>). 
      I'm a 
      <strong class="bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-600 to-red-600 dark:from-orange-400 dark:to-red-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
        Telecommunications and Electronic Engineer
      </strong> 
      who discovered programming through C++ and MySQL in college. 
      Today, I build institutional platforms at the University of Cienfuegos 
      and create modern, scalable web applications.
    </p>

    <div class="relative pl-6 border-l-3 border-orange-500 bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-50/50 to-transparent dark:from-orange-950/20 rounded-r-xl py-4 pr-4">
      <svg class="absolute -left-3 top-5 w-5 h-5 text-orange-500" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
      </svg>
      <p class="italic">
        <span class="font-semibold text-orange-700 dark:text-orange-300">🎯 Key achievement:</span><br/>
        I've contributed to optimizing the University of Cienfuegos' institutional platforms, 
        significantly improving performance, accessibility, and user experience for the entire community.
      </p>
    </div>

    {/* Tags */}
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 pt-2">
      <span class="px-3 py-1 text-xs sm:text-sm rounded-full bg-orange-100 dark:bg-orange-950/50 text-orange-700 dark:text-orange-300">🎓 Telecom Engineer</span>
      <span class="px-3 py-1 text-xs sm:text-sm rounded-full bg-orange-100 dark:bg-orange-950/50 text-orange-700 dark:text-orange-300">💻 Full-Stack Dev</span>
      <span class="px-3 py-1 text-xs sm:text-sm rounded-full bg-orange-100 dark:bg-orange-950/50 text-orange-700 dark:text-orange-300"> Cuba</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  {/* Imagen */}
  <div class="flex-1 flex justify-center order-1 lg:order-2">
    <div class="relative group">
      <div class="absolute -inset-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-400/20 to-red-500/20 rounded-full blur-2xl group-hover:blur-3xl transition-all"></div>
      <img
        width="280"
        height="280"
        src="/me.png"
        alt={personalImageAlt}
        class="relative w-56 h-56 sm:w-64 sm:h-64 md:w-72 md:h-72 object-cover rounded-2xl shadow-xl ring-4 ring-white dark:ring-gray-900 group-hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-500"
        style="object-position: 50% 50%"
        loading="lazy"
      />
      <div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-500 to-red-500 text-white px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-medium shadow-lg">
        Available
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</article>